data.description:
Offering $5000 seller concessions and a 1 year home warranty with acceptable offer!!! 
Beautiful, well maintained home in an established neighborhood! Energy efficient upgrades throughout the home, updated kitchen, new exterior paint, new roof and gutters! New garage door and motor were just installed, along with new exterior doors! Huge back deck with above ground pool, perfect for entertaining! Private backyard bordered with tall trees. Huge bonus room can also be used as a bedroom. Washer/Dryer and refrigerator to convey! Close to Clover, a mile from grocery and restaurants, and still only minutes from I85. And NO HOA!
